{
  "stem": "24409.8",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, so I went out, and I made myself consul of Liberia.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I bought stamps, consulate of Liberia.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I had even a sign on an office, which said consulate of Liberia.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And in order to make the British believe that this is genuine, so that they shouldn't go right away and say to the police that this is a forgery, I informed one [INAUDIBLE] and he was-- I forgot his name.",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I think his name was [INAUDIBLE] or [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And used the Hungarian name who wanted [INAUDIBLE] who was hanging around us to get information to bring it to the British.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And he would give information from the British to us.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "A very small guy.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And I told him, you know this is a very big thing.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "[INAUDIBLE] we can't tell you.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "It is a secret.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "But we tell you, it's a very big secret.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "We will get visas, as many as we want to.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "At the same time, I sent somebody to Belgrade.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "He didn't have to telephone this.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "That somebody should tell Belgrade-- let the British embassy in Belgrade know the same thing.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "[INAUDIBLE] let them know, confidentially, that we have the way now, to get visas en masse.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Because the message that we gave these two informers was that we are negotiating with a small Latin American country-- it was not Latin America-- but we said, with a small Latin American country, to appoint me as consul.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So the information came, and the British didn't act there, because this was not the idea of forgery.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Your forgeries are-- you'd be doing this in the basement, in the darkness.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And so I had-- I told it to everybody that I'm now consul.",
      "word_count": 13
    }
  ],
